22:49.627 --> 22:52.597
<i>RIDDICK: Somewhere along
the way, I lost a step.</i>

22:53.255 --> 22:55.053
<i>I got sloppy.</i>

22:55.675 --> 22:57.518
<i>Dulled my own edge.</i>

22:59.512 --> 23:02.607
<i>Maybe I went and did
the worst crime of all...</i>

23:04.225 --> 23:06.319
<i>I got civilized.</i>

23:13.150 --> 23:15.949
<i>So now we zero the clock.</i>

23:17.863 --> 23:21.208
<i>Just me and
this no-name world.</i>

23:24.036 --> 23:26.630
<i>Gotta find that
animal side again.</i>

